# Angular coding standards

Follow `docs/coding-standards/angular-coding-standards.md`. Styling: `tailwind-ui-styling` skill.

## Quick rules

- Standalone components; `inject()` for DI; signals for UI state
- `@if` / `@for` / `@switch` — not structural directives
- Feature-based Nx libs: `feature-*`, `data-access`, `ui`
- kebab-case file names; `readonly` on `input()` / `output()`
- `@floorganise/css` for styling; responsive utilities for layout
- `protected` for template-only members; thin lifecycle hooks
